author: Jorge Alonso
title: Cowboys Fan Gets Dropped By Giants Fan With One Punch During Tailgate Brawl
text:
Sometimes it’s best to just walk away. 
One Cowboys fan just couldn’t put his ego aside and went looking for a fight and ended up getting dropped against Giants fan during a tailgate during the Giants-Cowboys game from a few weeks ago. 

The Giants finished undefeated against the Cowboys on and off the field. 
H/T DailySnark
